spans.text: Pipe , or Sailors Crowd As sweetly echoes
like amorous Swains , When with alternate Loves they cheer the smiling Plains
tuneful Lay , Now whispering Breezes gentle
now the Halcyon builds her wavering Nest
the Deep overspread with stringy Weeds

The Manato his Change of Pleasure boasts ,
of the briny Main , Who want a Voice to sing , or — to complain
the distant Lowings of the Cow
that fluttering springs , And cuts the liquid Air with moistened Wings ; Strange is his Life , but stranger Laron's Fate , Who burns amid the Waves , and pines for Heat
Those gilded Flyers still in Danger move ,
The Nymph that's kind with Kindness must be paid
die ) But we those Dangers seek
that Passion , which they cannot hide
half the Deep , And pointed Rocks affright
